attributes.description: KMS key for accord ACL encrytion

attributes.name: accord-add-user-us-west-2-prod

attributes.rendered:
#!/bin/bash -v
sudo yum update -y aws-cfn-bootstrap
sudo yum update -y
sudo mkdir /vault
cd /vault
sudo aws s3 cp s3://"em-accord-vault-prod"/"zipfile.zip" "zipfile.zip"
sudo unzip "zipfile.zip"
sudo chmod +x scripts/vault_build_active.sh
sudo ./scripts/vault_build_active.sh "em-accord-vault-prod" "26b5449c-5eff-402e-b87c-d87ea659ed4a" "em-accord-vault-us-west-2-prod-dynamoDB" "https://consul.us-west-2.accord.ellieservices.com" "7e48f0db-cc55-02e8-10a8-30b3404b6b4f" "accord-prod-vault"
attributes.template:
#!/bin/bash -v
sudo yum update -y aws-cfn-bootstrap
sudo yum update -y
sudo mkdir /vault
cd /vault
sudo aws s3 cp s3://"${BUCKET}"/"${ZIPFILE}" "${ZIPFILE}"
sudo unzip "${ZIPFILE}"
sudo chmod +x scripts/vault_build_active.sh
sudo ./scripts/vault_build_active.sh "${BUCKET}" "${KMSKEY}" "${DYNAMO}" "${CONSUL}" "${CTOKEN}" "${LOGGROUPNAME}"
